ext-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold","children":"IRS 通知前 vs 通知后"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-brand-ink/75","children":[["$","ul","0",{"className":"space-y-2 list-disc pl-5","children":[["$","li","通知前：你可以主动提交 1040X 修正表并补齐表格。",{"children":"通知前：你可以主动提交 1040X 修正表并补齐表格。"}],["$","li","通知后：需要根据 IRS 通知内容回应，准备更多佐证材料。",{"children":"通知后：需要根据 IRS 通知内容回应，准备更多佐证材料。"}],["$","li","通知后处理周期更长，心理负担也更大。",{"children":"通知后处理周期更长，心理负担也更大。"}]]}]]}]]}],["$","section","如何撤销 Resident 申报-3",{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold","children":"如何撤销 Resident 申报"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-brand-ink/75","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"撤销居民申报通常意味着重新按非居民路径提交表格。你需要回到身份判断步骤，重新确认是否应走 1040-NR + 8843，并据此补充或替换材料。"}]]}]]}],["$","section","补缴情形与 IRS 罚款处理-4",{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold","children":"补缴情形与 IRS 罚款处理"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-brand-ink/75","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"如果修正后产生补缴，IRS 可能会要求补税或产生利息。IRS 罚款处理通常与申报时间和错误性质有关，不要忽视通知与截止日期。"}],["$","p","1",{"children":"提前准备材料、主动修正通常比被动回应更稳妥。即使没有罚款，也要保留所有寄送与沟通记录。"}]]}]]}],["$","section","邮寄与处理周期（参考）-5",{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold","children":"邮寄与处理周期（参考）"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-brand-ink/75","children":[["$","div","0",{"className":"overflow-x-auto rounded-[20px] border border-brand-pink/40 bg-white/90","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-left text-sm","children":[["$","thead",null,{"className":"bg-brand-pink/20 text-brand-ink","children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th","步骤",{"className":"px-4 py-3 font-semibold","children":"步骤"}],["$","th","动作",{"className":"px-4 py-3 font-semibold","children":"动作"}],["$","th","常见周期",{"className":"px-4 py-3 font-